Duplass Brothers Productions is an American independent film and television [[production company]] founded by [[Mark Duplass]] and [[Jay Duplass]], two brothers who are also actors, directors, producers and writers. They have produced films such as [[The Puffy Chair]] (2005), [[Safety Not Guaranteed]] (2012), [[The One I Love (film)|The One I Love]] (2014) and [[The Skeleton Twins]] (2014), and the [[HBO]] comedy-drama television series [[Togetherness (TV series)|Togetherness]] (2015–2016) and [[Room 104]] (2017-2020).
